{"tid":1656240,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"發洩文 我都唔知自己打撚左D乜野","createTime":"2019-10-15T13:19:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-15T13:33:58.000Z","uid":324194,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ef26bc65e1d63b897e96db40c74681f884abc0d4","tid":1656240,"uid":324194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T13:19:46.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大家對整個局勢冇一個好好既分析同共識<br />\n搞到大家既行動方針都出現左嚴重分歧</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n點樣做對整個運動有利<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />究竟國際戰線起到多大作用<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />美國係咪真係會搞死共產黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n-------------------------<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">回顧呢幾個月 佢地最驚D乜野?</span><br />\n佢地最驚就係<span style=\"color: blue;\">百萬人集會</span>，佢地最驚就係<span style=\"color: blue;\">真相</span><br />\n所以就不斷威嚇，用盡手段令人唔敢出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以佢地不斷擋鏡頭不斷妨礙拍攝<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成日見到人係到吵 乜撚野集會、乜野遍地開花 乜野爆舖 乜野武力、暴力<br />\n[日日話唔完美要改善 但係每次回過頭黎都又唔見有人討論點樣去改進、彌補缺點]<br />\n成日話乜撚野群眾智慧、獨立思考<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n除左搞藝術、做文宣、搞宣傳都唔見有活用過<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大規模集會不能完全不辨，但要靠民陣召集<br />\n要討論更多對策彌補缺點，令大規模集會更成功<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n係咩都冇做過既情況下，最重要既係唔好主動挑釁，喊口號、唱歌就好<br />\n等佢地主動開左第一發催淚彈驅散，就戴面罩 (和理非都戴個面罩啦好冇..)<br />\n對住催淚彈、橡膠彈 可以好似以往咁繼續用雨傘用面罩抵抗 盡量唔好退<br />\n<br />\n主要係對住一排POPO(睇落好多 但只有幾十人) <br />\n衝過黎個陣 大家(明明隔離有幾千個同伴，多POPO幾十倍)一定驚得後退<br />\n和平集會搞到更多人被捕，係因為兩「軍」對峙個陣，唔似打仗咁 有來有往<br />\n而係見到一排POPO 衝埋黎就退，呢個甚至完全唔能夠算係一個「對峙」<br />\n我地人多係最大既優勢 但人多亦係最大既缺點<br />\n我地百萬軍力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  人地3萬軍力<br />\n但係只有幾千勇武係到抵抗，仲要保護百萬個和理非去打仗 打撚 打屎忽?  <br />\n罵POPO就大聲，一D意義都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> POPO:「你咁做係唔會令我驚架」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n明明前排勇武仲驚，然後呢幾十萬班和理非就一個勁起哄恐慌，然後大撤退，立即潰不成軍。<br />\n結果就係走最尾典後既比人拉<br />\n呢個問題一日唔諗辨法解決，唔理你集中定遍地，都冇咩分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n反而覺得集會遊行冇咩用，令到人覺得 爆舖同打POPO反而仲有效果，更加落力去做<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">結果就係當一批人開始走向暴力，POPO既分化手段愈黎愈成功<br />\n[因為可以睇你班仆街為左呢D野係到日日吵]</span></span><br />\n佢地班人係咪以自己黑超特警，做左既野會係大家記憶消失既.....?<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">一日唔清算你班仆街，都跟你沒完</span></span><br />\n<br />\n因為有黨鐵、同中資舖既例子<br />\n然後可唔可以扮下野先做個儀式，發張通告講唔達到 某D 要求先搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 反正佢地都唔會答應<br />\n有時搞左先解釋，同宣告左有媒體報道 文宣做好之後搞，係天地之差 <br />\n做多少少功夫 遲少少先搞得唔得，明正言順 合情合理的搞 ，仲可以少D爭議<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;唔知算唔算改善方案&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n我覺得能走到今日，一開始會選擇抗爭呢條路<br />\n好大原因就係一開始有100萬人、200萬人，令大家有呢個勇氣，要守護呢個家<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n難聽D講 ，我地幾百萬人全部都要負上責任 <br />\n大家都驚，我都好撚驚<br />\n但係唔該真係有心要抗爭 可唔可以向前多走一步，鼓勵身邊既人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nPOPO衝埋黎都勇敢D企定唔好退，一人驚恐萬人慌<br />\n同POPO對峙 就攞彈弓、攞網球棍射水魔法<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢地要衝埋黎 就掉火魔法 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n要反擊，唔係D RT擺黎做乜撚野 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nRT應該用黎劃防線 唔係剩係擋一下既垃圾路障<br />\n如果擺黎剩係用黎撤退諗住可以用黎擋一擋POPO腳程既話不如唔好擺<br />\n和理非根本保護黎都哂氣 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n和理非同勇武本來就唔應該係一個固定既立場，而係隨時轉換既戰略<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n學下岳義士同Rider kick個位大佬啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲咁乖和理非都KAIKAI地，全部「切換」模式變勇武反擊啦屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依家咩時勢出得黎就預左被人打被拉 而且最危險最怕既係最前班年輕既<br />\n唔打得都學下「保護孩子」，剩係個人企係到都比到勇氣、比到力量其他人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n等POPO自己衝過黎，等佢地衝埋黎就係機會「反擊」，等佢地走近RT卡住 <br />\n然後拉佢地入黎，好似平時打落單狗咁打佢地個爽<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n退乜撚野 退屎忽，咁撚鍾意逃走一開始就唔好出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n龜係屋企，出得黎預左要面對POPO<br />\n要鼓勵身邊既人，唔係嚇身邊既人，勇敢D同POPO對峙<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1612031/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1612031/page/1</a><br />\n需要大量人手做彈弓同水魔法，或者可以用網球棍 用黎甩遠程魔法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1612376/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1612376/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;咁散會點算? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n冇左黨鐵，就準備替代品呀，就得黨鐵架咩依家，其他交通工具都死架<br />\n校巴呢，當初機場個堆接放學咩黎架<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;佢地會搜巴士 搜黨鐵喎?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你以為遍地開花佢就唔會搜架啦咩 <br />\n依家隨街見到著黑衫，樣後生都拉架啦 而且拉都唔輪到你啦仆街<br />\n佢地仲要專拉細路 一班變態<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不如另外多諗D辨法保護班細路仲好啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外要做敢死隊既話 <br />\n最好就係搵辨法捉隻大陸武警<br />\n或者調查、追蹤新屋嶺同自殺案(公開求真相 完全沒用，要地底查)<br />\n<br />\n而唔係去殺POPO，殺左背後個共產黨就偷笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n問題係依家比你打撚死一隻狗 自己爽，然後搞垮成個運動好D<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n定係 諗辨法將佢地全部清算 大家一齊爽好D 到時你想點打都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n-------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n中共一直解決唔到<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">美國</span>同<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">香港</span>既問題<br />\n依家天降左個<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">NBA</span>同<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">暴雪</span>，仲自爆作死送分 <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有冇辨法 製造幾條戰線、搞大D， 搞到佢四面楚歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span><br />\nNBA 搬出黎 暴雪 搬出黎 聲援言論自由 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n維持住條戰線，睇下有冇其他突然又從天而降 <br />\n依家應該好多人好不爽，話唔定又有其他行業既名人肯出黎發句聲，然後佢地就發起抵制自爆 <br />\n將共產黨最忌諱個堆都攞出黎鞭就岩架啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n器官活摘<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  國際獨立法庭裁定中共反人類<br />\n新疆問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 依家人權法案過左，會實施制裁 搬埋出黎聲援新疆人權<br />\n<br />\n香港同美國既問題其實已經掛勾係一齊，我覺得唔駛太擔心現屆美國政府會賣港<br />\n人權法案既作用應該唔會好大，但或許會提供一D機會比我地做野<br />\n美國係一定會搞中共，當然係基於美國利益，同面對中國威脅既考量，其他國家可能也會參與，依家國際間背後有好多小動作，好多都唔係偶然發生，但睇黎一切仲係籌備階段。<br />\n呢方面雖然唔輪到我地控制，但一定要諗辨法不失國際支持，抗爭落去<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?time_continue=2&amp;v=vSEhHcFMRbo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Ftime_continue%3D2%26v%3DvSEhHcFMRbo&d=uOCBXhtcaqxtHROYLuBCLD632Ab34%2FJQlYP9Mjrnz38%3D&h=399c6793\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?time_continue=2&amp;v=vSEhHcFMRbo</a><br />\n唔好聽都要講句，同中共比武力，打從一開始就冇贏面。更不用說香港打既係傀儡<br />\n中共呢個政權係一個全球化既新產物，歷史個堆抗爭同革命既例子唔好意思真係唔適用<br />\n<br />\n點解美國一定會搞中共<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=aBBX1Z2TYb8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DaBBX1Z2TYb8&d=uOCBXhtcaqxtHROYLuBCLD632Ab34%2FJQlYP9Mjrnz38%3D&h=b703c9a2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=aBBX1Z2TYb8</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/Q7SYRkosumosu/status/1183183933111799808\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FQ7SYRkosumosu%2Fstatus%2F1183183933111799808&d=uOCBXhtcaqxtHROYLuBCLD632Ab34%2FJQlYP9Mjrnz38%3D&h=f35dd442\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FQ7SYRkosumosu%2Fstatus%2F1183183933111799808&h=59b2e901\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/Q7SYRkosumosu/status/1183183933111799808</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-ohK5adNi4k\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D-ohK5adNi4k&d=uOCBXhtcaqxtHROYLuBCLD632Ab34%2FJQlYP9Mjrnz38%3D&h=e2173263\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-ohK5adNi4k</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=DOFwxcb0Bjc&amp;t=132s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DDOFwxcb0Bjc%26t%3D132s&d=uOCBXhtcaqxtHROYLuBCLD632Ab34%2FJQlYP9Mjrnz38%3D&h=ece637eb\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=DOFwxcb0Bjc&amp;t=132s</a><br />\n<br />\n然後凱爾巴斯說了一堆關於中國經濟問題，只是我完全聽不懂<br />\n<br />\n而且依家有NBA、Blizzard 事件；另一邊斯伯丁將軍跟比爾格茨的新書<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FurxpUM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFurxpUM.jpg&h=bb9a3d48&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/h7CgRzT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fh7CgRzT.png&h=dabfc217&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n令美國民眾覺醒，瞭解真相，也有著反共思想同情緒。"},{"pid":"93c46ccf940f57cf2e7e409e1ec46e1ab41a3bf8","tid":1656240,"uid":324194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T13:24:07.000Z","msg":"避免誤會   呢到更正一下<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">[因為可以睇你班仆街為左呢D野係到日日吵]</span><br />\n呢班係罵各位<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢邊係罵政府罵POPO <br />\n佢地班人係咪以自己黑超特警，做左既野會係大家記憶消失既.....?<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">一日唔清算你班仆街，都跟你沒完<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"872f61d6abd600af0c454dc4f0d77888485087b2","tid":1656240,"uid":331173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T13:25:14.000Z","msg":"唔係亂打喎巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />推唔郁都推<br />\n<br />\n一條片解釋為何無法和藍屍溝通<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1656168\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1656168</a>"},{"pid":"bf55809e190ba4614bfb2dfc0a0508a3580e7f88","tid":1656240,"uid":324194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T13:25:55.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">和理非同勇武本來就唔應該係一個固定既立場，而係隨時轉換既戰略</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">和理非同勇武本來就唔應該係一個固定既立場，而係隨時轉換既戰略</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">和理非同勇武本來就唔應該係一個固定既立場，而係隨時轉換既戰略</span></span>"},{"pid":"5fd3b8c0f639a9ba180e00ff264bb5631004a7e4","tid":1656240,"uid":324194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T13:33:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/GlobalHimalaya/status/1184082745972146176\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FGlobalHimalaya%2Fstatus%2F1184082745972146176&d=uOCBXhtcaqxtHROYLuBCLD632Ab34%2FJQlYP9Mjrnz38%3D&h=e7e381f4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FGlobalHimalaya%2Fstatus%2F1184082745972146176&h=395d8c01\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/GlobalHimalaya/status/1184082745972146176</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=yvowPDJ836E \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DyvowPDJ836E%20&d=uOCBXhtcaqxtHROYLuBCLD632Ab34%2FJQlYP9Mjrnz38%3D&h=a11cbbbc\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.yout